Global Financial Services Buyout










 









 Overview


The Carlyle Global Financial Services Buyout team invests in management buyouts, growth capital opportunities and strategic minority investments in financial services.





Carlyle Global Financial Services Partners







Launched in 2008 at $1.1 billion, this fund invests in management buyouts, growth capital opportunities and strategic minority investments in financial services.









