Company Overview of Carlyle Global Financial Services Partners, L.P.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Carlyle Global Financial Services Partners, L.P. specializes in management buyouts, distressed debt, middle market, growth capital opportunities. The fund primarily invests in the financial services sectors. It invests around the world. It makes strategic minority investments and also prefers to take majority stake in its portfolio companies.


1001 Pennsylvania Avenue, NWWashington, DC 20004United StatesFounded in 2008



Phone: 202-729-5626

Fax: 202-347-1818

